Version 2.7-unreleased
======================

* configure Wendy with `--enable-syslog' to additionally write verbose
  output to the syslog (e.g. `/var/log/system.log')

* `--reportFrequency' sets the number of edges to be reported (was: number
  of knowledges)


See file ChangeLog <http://service-technology.org/files/wendy/ChangeLog> for
complete version history.

